(147, 'See', 'A virus has decimated humankind. Those who survived emerged blind. Centuries later when twins are born with the mythic ability to see, their father must protect his tribe against a threatened queen.', 'returning', '8.1', '57.06', 'Drama / Sci-Fi / Fantasy / Action / Adventure', '2019-11-01', '2019-12-06', 'see-80752.jpg', 'see-80752.jpg', 80752, '2020-11-27 11:51:06', NULL),
